<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#999900">Originally posted by Tiberius on 10-12-1999 06:06 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Well there *IS* a way to get a anvil and forge into your pack, and it is still around.  The bad part is I do not know how to do it, or have been able to recreate it.  I was macroing making weapons while working on my first GM Smithy when I came back to unload my weapons due to being over weight I see a forge and anvil in my main pack....I cleared out the weapons and the anvil and forge were fully functional, only bad thing is they weighed over 400 stones and made it rather difficult to walk.  I tried to remove them from my pack with no success.  This bug is still around and I believe that is has to do with lag, i was stuck in my spot and had to page a GM to remove it from my pack, I asked the GM how it happened and he stated it was a mix of lag on the server and me doing alot at once.... You guys can try, i know it is till out there but am unable to get it to happen again....

